tip.text: Can't decide which flavour I like the most! They are all so good! Hands down best cupcake ever.
Love the crunchy french toast, adding an additional maple syrup on the side would be good.
Loving the crawfish beignet & fried chicken!
Bread butter pudding is way overrated. Too mushy and it should be warm instead of room temp. Tasted better one in Singapore.
Must try: salted egg yolk donuts!
Loving the seared wagyu ribeye with crispy rice patty, seaweed salsa verde & herb salad. 👌🏻
